    "title": "create saas college register website",
    "prompt": "create saas college register website",
    "html": "<html lang=\"en\">\n<head>\n    <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n    <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n    <title>College Register SaaS</title>\n    <style>\n        /* Global styles */\n        * {\n            margin: 0;\n            padding: 0;\n            box-sizing: border-box;\n        }\n        body {\n            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;\n            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1e1e1e, #131313);\n            color: #fff;\n            line-height: 1.6;\n            overflow-x: hidden;\n        }\n        a {\n            color: inherit;\n            text-decoration: none;\n            transition: color 0.3s ease;\n        }\n        a:hover {\n            color: #1DBF73;\n        }\n        .container {\n            max-width: 1200px;\n            margin: auto;\n            padding: 0 2rem;\n        }\n\n        /* Navbar */\n        nav {\n            background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.7);\n            backdrop-filter: blur(5px);\n            padding: 1rem 0;\n            position: fixed;\n            width: 100%;\n            z-index: 10;\n        }\n        .nav-bar {\n            display: flex;\n            justify-content: space-between;\n            align-items: center;\n        }\n        .nav-bar ul {\n            list-style: none;\n            display: flex;\n            gap: 1.5rem;\n        }\n\n        /* Hero Section */\n        .hero {\n            height: 100vh;\n            display: flex;\n            align-items: center;\n            justify-content: center;\n            text-align: center;\n            background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1), rgba(255, 255, 255, 0));\n        }\n        .hero-content {\n            max-width: 800px;\n            animation: fadeIn 2s ease-out;\n        }\n        .hero h1 {\n            font-size: 3.5rem;\n            margin-bottom: 1rem;\n            background: linear-gradient(to right, #1DBF73, #00b4d8);\n            -webkit-background-clip: text;\n            -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;\n        }\n        .hero p {\n            font-size: 1.25rem;\n            margin-bottom: 2rem;\n        }\n        .hero .cta {\n            padding: 0.75rem 1.5rem;\n            border: none;\n            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1DBF73, #00b4d8);\n            border-radius: 5px;\n            cursor: pointer;\n            transition: background 0.3s ease;\n        }\n        .hero .cta:hover {\n            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #00b4d8, #1DBF73);\n        }\n\n        /* Features Section */\n        .features {\n            padding: 5rem 0;\n            background: rgba(35, 35, 35, 0.9);\n        }\n        .features .feature-item {\n            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05);\n            backdrop-filter: blur(5px);\n            padding: 2rem;\n            border-radius: 10px;\n            box-shadow: 0 8px 16px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);\n            transition: transform 0.3s ease;\n        }\n        .features .feature-item:hover {\n            transform: translateY(-10px);\n        }\n        .features h2 {\n            text-align: center;\n            margin-bottom: 2rem;\n            font-size: 2.5rem;\n        }\n        .features-grid {\n            display: grid;\n            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr));\n            gap: 2rem;\n        }\n\n        /* Testimonials Section */\n        .testimonials {\n            padding: 5rem 0;\n            text-align: center;\n        }\n        .testimonials .testimonial-item {\n            max-width: 400px;\n            margin: auto;\n            margin-bottom: 2rem;\n            padding: 1.5rem;\n            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05);\n            border-radius: 10px;\n        }\n\n        /* Pricing Section */\n        .pricing {\n            padding: 5rem 0;\n            background: rgba(50, 50, 50, 0.9);\n        }\n        .pricing h2 {\n            text-align: center;\n            margin-bottom: 2rem;\n        }\n        .pricing-grid {\n            display: grid;\n            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(200px, 1fr));\n            gap: 2rem;\n        }\n        .pricing-item {\n            padding: 2rem;\n            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05);\n            border-radius: 10px;\n            text-align: center;\n            transition: transform 0.3s ease;\n        }\n        .pricing-item:hover {\n            transform: translateY(-10px);\n        }\n\n        /* CTA Section */\n        .cta-section {\n            padding: 5rem 0;\n            text-align: center;\n            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1DBF73, #00b4d8);\n            color: #000;\n        }\n        .cta-section .cta-button {\n            margin-top: 2rem;\n            padding: 0.75rem 1.5rem;\n            border: none;\n            background: #fff;\n            border-radius: 5px;\n            cursor: pointer;\n            transition: background 0.3s ease;\n        }\n        .cta-section .cta-button:hover {\n            background: #e9e9e9;\n        }\n\n        /* Footer */\n        footer {\n            padding: 2rem 0;\n            text-align: center;\n            background: #101010;\n        }\n\n        /* Animations */\n        @keyframes fadeIn {\n            from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(10px); }\n            to { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }\n        }\n    </style>\n</head>\n<body>\n    <nav>\n        <div class=\"container nav-bar\">\n            <div class=\"logo\"><a href=\"#\">College Register</a></div>\n            <ul>\n                <li><a href=\"#\">Features</a></li>\n                <li><a href=\"#\">Pricing</a></li>\n                <li><a href=\"#\">Testimonials</a></li>\n                <li><a href=\"#\">Contact</a></li>\n            </ul>\n        </div>\n    </nav>\n\n    <section class=\"hero\">\n        <div class=\"container hero-content\">\n            <h1>Empower Your College Management</h1>\n            <p>Streamline your college's administration with our cutting-edge SaaS solution designed for efficiency and productivity.</p>\n            <button class=\"cta\">Get Started</button>\n        </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <section class=\"features\">\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <h2>Features</h2>\n            <div class=\"features-grid\">\n                <div class=\"feature-item\">\n                    <h3>Automated Scheduling</h3>\n                    <p>Intelligently schedule classes and manage timetables with ease.</p>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"feature-item\">\n                    <h3>Student Management</h3>\n                    <p>Effortlessly manage student records, attendance, and grades.</p>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"feature-item\">\n                    <h3>Billing & Payments</h3>\n                    <p>Simplify fee collection and track financial transactions seamlessly.</p>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <section class=\"testimonials\">\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <h2>What People Are Saying</h2>\n            <div class=\"testimonial-item\">\n                <p>\"Our administration process has never been smoother since switching to this platform. Highly recommend!\"</p>\n                <strong>- John Doe, College Administrator</strong>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <section class=\"pricing\">\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <h2>Pricing</h2>\n            <div class=\"pricing-grid\">\n                <div class=\"pricing-item\">\n                    <h3>Basic</h3>\n                    <p>Free</p>\n                    <ul>\n                        <li>Up to 50 students</li>\n                        <li>Email support</li>\n                    </ul>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"pricing-item\">\n                    <h3>Standard</h3>\n                    <p>$49/mo</p>\n                    <ul>\n                        <li>Up to 500 students</li>\n                        <li>Phone support</li>\n                        <li>Advanced features</li>\n                    </ul>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"pricing-item\">\n                    <h3>Premium</h3>\n                    <p>$99/mo</p>\n                    <ul>\n                        <li>Unlimited students</li>\n                        <li>24/7 support</li>\n                        <li>All features</li>\n                    </ul>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <section class=\"cta-section\">\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <h2>Ready to Transform Your College?</h2>\n            <p>Join thousands of institutions unlocking new efficiencies.</p>\n            <button class=\"cta-button\">Try It Now</button>\n        </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <footer>\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <p>&copy; 2023 College Register. All rights reserved.</p>\n        </div>\n    </footer>\n</body>\n</html>",
    "createdAt": "2026-05-10T06:15:18.169Z",
    "visibility": "private"
  }
]